  "text": "Statistical analyses for the core have been reported previously [CITATION_1] . For the primary efficacy analysis, the proportion of patients who reached LIC <5 mg Fe/g dw by the end of the extension is presented with a 95 % confidence interval (Wilson CI) [CITATION_2] . For data analyses presented by average actual dose, patients were summarized by the dose category regardless of their treatment groups. Descriptive statistics were used to present efficacy analyses. Compliance was reported as planned dose taken= 100×cumulative dose taken/cumulative planned dose.",
